data.description:
THIS HOME WILL CHARM YOU! IT IS QUAINT AND BEAUTIFUL. ALL ORIGINAL ARCHITECTURE AND FEATURES IN PRISTINE CONDITION. FRENCH DOORS,ORIGINAL WOOD FLOORS, ORIGINAL CROWN MOLDING, BUILT IN BOOKCASE MANTLE AND KITCHEN BUFFET ALSO FEATURES A LARGE SEPARATE FORMAL DINING ROOM (can be used as a study or card room) LARGE BEDROOMS AND LARGE BATH AND CLOSETS. A NEW WOOD BUILT LARGE DECK IN BACK AND COVERED PATIO DECK IN FRONT, A 2 CAR DETACHED GARAGE WITH STORAGE. ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDING REFRIGERATOR, WASHER AND DRYER INCLUDED IN THE PRICE OF THE RENT. THIS WON'T LAST LONG. PERFECT FOR RETIRED COUPLE OR MATURE COUPLE WITH BABY. NO CRIMINAL RECORD, NO EVICTIONS OR BANKRUPCY CANDIDATES PLEASE. DON'T WAIT IF THIS SOUNDS LIKE YOUR CHARM YOU MUST COME SEE!

Must have govt photo Id and copies of 2 paystubs. Additionally, must be able to pass a credit, criminal and background check. No evictions please
data.whatILove: This home is charming with original wood floors in great condition. Original crown moldings and casings as well as built ins. Rare double car garage and farm sink. Granite kitchen and large formal dining room enclosed in french doors. Beautiful attached deck
